data.text:
SCF Music Program

Jazz Orchestra and Jazz Messengers Combo

March 21, 2024 @ 7:30pm

SCF Neel Performing Arts Center, Bldg. 11 East

“From the moment Tony Bennett met her he knew she was special.” Join the SCF Jazz Orchestra, with American Songbook master crooner Bryan J. Hughes and vocal starlet Savannah Brady in a one-night tribute to the one-night collaboration between Tony Bennett and Amy Winehouse. From London to New York, the paths of these iconic singers crossed for a historic recording session of American Songbook classics. Dr. Pete Carney directs this show, which promises a profound homage and a big band beating heart that was “left in San Francisco.”

Visit scf.edu/music and check out SCF Music on Facebook.
